            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-e09200-Hd1e108">Rubrica 12</head>
            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-e09200-Hd1e111" type="question-title">De humana consolatione miserorum</head>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-e09200-d1e114">
               <lb ed="#V" n="60"/>
      ¶ De humana consolatione min
      <lb ed="#V" n="61" break="no"/>serorum. Rubrica. 12.
    </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-e09200-d1e121">
               <lb ed="#V" n="62"/>hyst. c. 2. Quidam ami
      <lb ed="#V" n="63"/>Ob cus iob noine elipham: con
      <lb ed="#V" n="64"/>solatus fuit iob in aduersitatibus su
      <lb ed="#V" n="65"/>is his verbis: Docuisti multos: et ma
      <lb ed="#V" n="66"/>nus lapsas roborasti: vacillantes confirmaue
      <lb ed="#V" n="67"/>runt sermones tui: et genua trementia confor
      <lb ed="#V" n="68"/>tasti. Nunc autem venit super te plaga: et
      <lb ed="#V" n="69"/>defecisti: tetegit te deus et conturbatus es:
      <lb ed="#V" n="70"/>vbi est timor tuus: fortitudo tua: et perfe
      <lb ed="#V" n="71" break="no"/>fectio manuum tuarum: Recordare obse
      <lb ed="#V" n="72" break="no"/>cro te quis vnquam inuocens periit: aut quan
      <lb ed="#V" n="73" break="no"/>do recti deleti sunt: quinpotius vidi eos quie
      <lb ed="#V" n="74"/>operantur iniquitatem et seminant dolores
      <lb ed="#V" n="75"/>et metunt eos flante deo perisse: et spiritu ire
      <lb ed="#V" n="76"/>eius esse consumptos. 
    </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-e09200-d1e156">
               <lb ed="#V" n="77"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-e09200-Qd1e160">¶ Cronica de nugis philosophorum. c. 4 scilicet
        <lb ed="#V" n="78"/>de chilone. Chilo lacedemonius qui fuit
        <lb ed="#V" n="79"/>vnus de. vii. sapiententibus iubebat citius ad ca
        <lb ed="#V" n="80" break="no"/>lamitates amicorum quam ad prosperitates ire. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-e09200-d1e171">
               <lb ed="#V" n="81"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-e09200-Qd1e175">¶ Iesus filius sirach: in ecclesiast. c. 7.
        <lb ed="#V" n="82"/>Non desis plorantibus in consolatione. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-e09200-d1e181">
               <lb ed="#V" n="83"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-e09200-Qd1e185">¶ Quidius de tristibus. vel. 5. e. 9.
        <lb ed="#V" n="84"/>Detineo studiis animum: falloque dolores
        <lb ed="#V" n="85"/>Experior: curis et dare verba meis. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-e09200-d1e193">
               <lb ed="#V" n="86"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-e09200-Qd1e197">/ Idem methamorph. l. 15. et fina.
        <lb ed="#V" n="87"/>Neque enim fortuna querenda.
        <lb ed="#V" n="88"/>Sola tua est: similes aliorum respice casus
        <lb ed="#V" n="89"/>Mitius insta feres: vtinamque exempla dolentem
        <lb ed="#V" n="90"/>Non mea te posset releuare: sed et mea possuit. <!--324.xml-->
        <pb ed="#V" n="143-r"/>
                  <cb ed="#V" n="a"/>
               </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-e09200-d1e216">
               <lb ed="#V" n="1"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-e09200-Qd1e220">¶ Seneca de tranquillitate animi: Si te ad
        <lb ed="#V" n="2"/>studia reuocaueris: omne vite fastidium effugies </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-e09200-d1e226">
               <lb ed="#V" n="3"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-e09200-Qd1e230">/ Idem de consolatione ad paulinum: Studia
        <lb ed="#V" n="4"/>optime felicitatem extollunt: et facilime ca
        <lb ed="#V" n="5" break="no"/>lamitatem minuunt.
        <lb ed="#V" n="6"/>Uartus et vltimus liber quin
        <lb ed="#V" n="7"/>ite partis tractat de morali com
        <lb ed="#V" n="8"/>sideratione vite et mortis sub
        <lb ed="#V" n="9"/>his titulis. </quote>
            </p>
